    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Deprecate the LspProgress autocommand event in favor of the newer, more generic, `Progress` event.\n\nWe need to find a way to do this that follows the deprecation policy.",
    "closed_at": null,
    "closed_by": null,
    "comment_data": [
