            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "cc @mfussenegger @MariaSolOs @lewis6991 Does this make sense? Is there a use case for keeping `LspProgress` separate from `Progress`? If so, should we have the default `$/progress` handler fire both the `LspProgress` and `Progress` events?",
